{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/performances/pronunciation/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"  <div class=\"box\">\n      <div class=\"dscrptn\">\n        Recently I was studying English and found that many words I don't know how to pronounced. This reminds me when I was a child, some students would add phonetic spelling to English words that they could not read, so I became a little interested in the pronunciation system. This time I used the phonetic of Chinese as the sound Develop and proceed in a unitary manner. Explain the common phenomena of Chinese pronunciation including Chinese-English comparison, \"an, on\" without distinction, tongue curling... At the same time I tried different operations from my previous audio visual performances, driving the behavior record by sound.<br>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n<div class=\"box\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/f1d9a/img1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 58.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"img1\" title=\"img1\" src=\"/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/c1b63/img1.png\" srcset=\"/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/5a46d/img1.png 300w,\n/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/0a47e/img1.png 600w,\n/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/c1b63/img1.png 1200w,\n/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/d61c2/img1.png 1800w,\n/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/97a96/img1.png 2400w,\n/static/1c2e58e3671c0a437a3aafd4473a8ffe/f1d9a/img1.png 2710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"box\">\n      <div class=\"dscrptn\">\n        最近在念英文，發現有許多單字不會念，於是想到小時候有些同學會在不會念的英文單字上加上注音的拼法，因此開始對發音系統感到有點興趣，這次以中文的注音作為聲響發展，單元式的進行，闡述中文發音常有的現象包括中英對照、ㄢㄤ不分、捲舌......，同時嘗試了不同於我以往音像表演中的操作，以聲音驅動行為紀錄的影像<br>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"box\"></div>\n  <iframe title=\"vimeo-player\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/548516085\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>","frontmatter":{"title":"Pronunciation Exercise","date":"2021","category":"Audio visual performance","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/f7f2618821ef02beeee8feea9f2a00a1/ddb6f/img-0.png","srcSet":"/static/f7f2618821ef02beeee8feea9f2a00a1/d734b/img-0.png 750w,\n/static/f7f2618821ef02beeee8feea9f2a00a1/ddb6f/img-0.png 800w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/f7f2618821ef02beeee8feea9f2a00a1/59596/img-0.webp 750w,\n/static/f7f2618821ef02beeee8feea9f2a00a1/96b3c/img-0.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.625}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/performances/pronunciation/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}